These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-1::.
There 7 different types of food: peas, potato, artichoke, mango, kiwi, spinach, pomegranate
1. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person eating potato##1
2. the person eating peas is on the left of the person eating mango##1
3. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
4. the person eating kiwi is between the person eating peas and the person eating artichoke##2
5. the person eating mango is between the person eating potato and the person eating peas##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3   |    4    |  5  |   6   |   7   |
| Food   | pomegranate | artichoke | kiwi | peas | mango | potato | spinach |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-2::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: taxi, van, snowmobile, skateboard, boat, motorbike, airplane
1. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
2. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
4. the person driving the snowmobile is between the person driving the skateboard and the person driving the taxi##2
5. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the van##1
6. the person driving the snowmobile is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |   3    |   4   |     5      |    6    |     7      |
| Transport   | motorbike | airplane | taxi | snowmobile | skateboard | van | boat |

