.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-3::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: fanta, water, tea, lemonade, almond-milk, juice, coffee
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
2. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
3. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
4. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
5. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
6. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person drinking juice and the person drinking water##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |   3    |     4      |   5    |    6    |   7    |
| Beverage   | coffee | juice | almond-milk | water | fanta | tea | lemonade |

