2. the person eating cabbage is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
3. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person eating apple##1
4. the person eating cabbage is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
5. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person eating apple##1
6. the person eating peach is in the middle##1
7. the person eating kale is the person eating kale##1
8. the person eating carrot is on the left of the person eating kale##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |    3    |      4      |    5    |    6    |    7    |
| Food   | cabbage | apricot | cucumber | peach | apple | carrot | kale |

