.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-5::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: dubstep, trance, pop, metal, ambient, reggae, house
1. the fan reggae is between the fan metal and the fan ambient##2
2. the fan dubstep is on the far right##1
3. the fan metal is the fan metal##1
4. the fan trance is on the left of the fan dubstep##1
5. the fan house is on the far left##1
6. the fan pop is between the fan ambient and the fan trance##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |      4       |   5   |     6     |   7    |
| Music-Genre   | house | metal | reggae | ambient | pop | trance | dubstep |

