2. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1
3. the person who likes orange is the person who likes orange##1
4. the person who likes fuchsia is between the person who likes turquise and the person who likes orange##2
5. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the person who likes green##1
6. the person who likes brown is between the person who likes mauve and the person who likes turquise##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |   3   |   4    |   5    |      6       |     7     |
