3. the prince-smoker is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
4. the blend-smoker is between the aristoff-smoker and the dunhill-smoker##2
5. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1   |     2      |   3    |   4    |   5    |   6    |    7     |
| Cigar   | swisher | dunhill | blend | aristoff | prince | montecristo | siglo |

