.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-20::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: aquamarine, chestnut, lavender, turquise, ivory, yellow, white
1. the person who likes white is in the middle##1
2. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1
3. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person who likes white##1
4. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
5. the person who likes turquise is between the person who likes white and the person who likes lavender##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2     |   3    |    4    |     5      |   6    |  7  |
| Color   | aquamarine | chestnut | ivory | white | turquise | lavender | yellow |

 